Here is the JavaScript code to calculate the factorial of x:

```javascript
let x = 7;
let result = 1;

for (let i = 1; i <= x; i++) {
    result *= i;
}

console.log("The factorial of " + x + " is " + result);
```

This script assigns the value 7 to the variable x, then iterates from 1 to x, multiplying the running total to find the final factorial value.
